    "Body": " Our client is a global Blockchain Asset firm that is currently seeking to appoint a competent and organised Director of Communication to be based in Lugano, Switzerland. Become a part of far-sighted business that improves both technology and user experience through a methodological approach that is inspired by an ever dynamic world - both in technology and application used-friendliness. You will be responsible for the formulation of a business-wide communication externally and internally as well as achieving targets and specific goals with the information produced from the company. The Director of Communication will regularly assess the effectiveness of the business\u2019s communication channels and work on solution for improvement and development. The Director will also conduct analyses on audience segmentation, key messages, communication schedules etc., and report findings directly to the Chief Marketing Officer and key stakeholders. Requirements: - Ideally you have at least 10 years experience working in leadership position. - You have a strong and demonstrable knowledge and experience in Marketing and Communication at an International level. - You are familiar with Cryptocurrency and curious about new technologies. - You are experienced in managing information flows both internally and externally. - You possess a strong understanding of leadership. You are able to inspire and lead colleagues during stressful and demanding periods. - You have exceptional verbal and written skills. - You have an advanced degree in Communications, Marketing, Business Administration or any other related field. - You have a high level of analytical and technological skills as well as you can negotiate and build strong relationships within and outside the business. - You will be able to work strategically to achieve targets and specific goals. - Your English and Italian languages are both at professional level. The company offers a highly competitive remuneration and bonuses. If you are interested in this role and feel you might be suitable, we would like to hear from you! Please send us your recent CV and a covering letter. Skills Communication, Italian, English, Marketing Compensation Competitive Applications for this job are currently closed. ", 
